name: sky fall 03
description: [a video score for the sky. @yidan_zeng]  sky • body • water • fall (天 • 体 • 水 • 落) is an invitation and meditation on presence, existing as a two-channel archive of past migration and present movement through video collages and spoken scores. What if we connected through the natureverse instead of the Internet? By interfacing with our bodies and nature as portals for connection, we may just find ourselves together across distance. Full video and audio scores available after purchase.
